{"SELJUKIAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to Seljuk, a Tartar chief who embraced Mohammedanism, and began the subjection of Western Asia to that faith and rule; of or pertaining to the dynasty founded by him, or the empire maintained by his descendants from the 10th to the 13th century.","pos":""},{"def":"A member of the family of Seljuk; an adherent of that family, or subject of its government; (pl.","pos":""}]}